This is happening because each FITS file in `auxiliary_files` is actually an `HDUList` and not single `HDU`s. The hacky way around this is to do something like this in your modifications:

```python
if isinstance(fits_file, _astropy.pyfits.ImageHDU):
    f = [fits_file]
elif isinstance(fits_file, _astropy.pyfits.HDUList):
    f = fits_file
else:
```

But we can probably think of a better way to do this at some point.
